column4: waypoint_clicker subscribes to an unpublished topic: '/clicked_point'. But there is a publisher(s) error_reproducer that publishes a similar message type: geometry_msgs/PoseWithCovarianceStamped as /initialpose. waypoint_clicker was launched by /.dockerinstall/waypoint_clicker.launch

error_reproducer  publishes to an unsubscribed topic: '/initialpose'. But there is a subscriber(s) waypoint_clicker._clicked_point_sub with a similar name that subscribes to a similar message type. error_reproducer was launched from /ros_ws/reproduce.launch.
